                        solution: "s = 1.8 × 10⁻¹⁰ / 0.100 = 1.8 × 10⁻⁹ mol dm⁻³",
                        comparison: "Solubility in pure water = 1.34 × 10⁻⁵ mol dm⁻³; in NaCl solution = 1.8 × 10⁻⁹ mol dm⁻³ — reduced by factor of ~7000"
