                    belowTransitionTemp: "G(solid) < G(liquid) → solid is stable",
                    aboveTransitionTemp: "G(liquid) < G(solid) → liquid is stable",
                    generalPrinciple: "The phase with lowest G is the stable phase at given T and P"
