                    "ICE: [H⁺] = x; Ka = x²/(0.30−x) ≈ x²/0.30",
                    "x = √(1.8×10⁻⁴ × 0.30) = √(5.4×10⁻⁵) = 7.35×10⁻³ M",
                    "Check: 7.35×10⁻³/0.30 × 100% = 2.45% < 5% ✓",
                    "pH = −log(7.35×10⁻³) = 2.13"
